title: Relet in WaHu apartments
posting_body: ['*****$750 incentive upon signed relet*****', 'LISTING:', 'One bedroom, one bathroom in Stadium Village in September *$750 bonus upon relet completion*', 'I am listing one bedroom with it’s own connected bathroom for relet.', 'This is a separate lease within a four bedroom, four bathroom apartment at WaHu, located above Blaze pizza, directly in front of Huntington Bank Stadium.', 'Each bedroom has it’s own separate lease, and out of four of the people planning on leasing one will not be returning to the U of M next year.', 'Lease begins September 3, 2022.', 'Shared living space, kitchen and in-apartment laundry and drying.', 'Building amenities include gym, pool and secured entrance.', 'Spots are available.', 'The apartment is unit #548 and rent is $825 per month and utilities are separate.', 'Utilities estimate from $50-$70 monthly.', 'Please reach out of you have any questions about the apartment, reletting process or anything else!', 'Please contact the WaHu building directly for tours!']
